1. *Lik* je bio potpuno misteriozan. (The figure was completely mysterious.)
2. Ona je stvorila *lik* u svom umu. (She created a figure in her mind.)
3. Oni su se poistovetili sa *likom* koji je bio na slici. (They identified themselves with the figure that was in the picture.)
4. Ona je otkrila *lik* u magli. (She discovered a figure in the fog.)
5. Njegov *lik* se pojavljivao u mnogim pesmama. (His figure appeared in many songs.)
6. On je bio neko ko je imao vrlo poseban *lik*. (He was someone who had a very special character.)